00:35:25,430 --> 00:35:26,429
Speaker 1: Moving around, shooting around.

588
00:35:26,510 --> 00:35:32,670
Speaker 0: Moving around, shooting around and it's a simple control, but the actual game is very advanced and complex.

589
00:35:32,850 --> 00:35:36,010
Speaker 0: You have to move in complex patterns and see what's coming up.

590
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:49,008
Speaker 0: In a way, it's sort of like DDR and you have these arrows coming at you and you have to sort of push these very few buttons in a pattern, you know, in a correct way that you can match the pattern.

591
00:35:49,370 --> 00:35:58,970
